<paragraph blockId="5.[212,321,783,807]" box="[212,321,783,807]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1913">
<emphasis box="[212,321,783,807]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="1913">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[212,1172,823,879]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1913">
Tenth sternite broadened distally, deeply separated basally (
<figureCitation box="[860,968,823,847]" captionStart="Figures 8–14" captionStartId="5.[212,289,1586,1608]" captionTargetBox="[212,1172,905,1543]" captionTargetId="figure-176@5.[212,1172,903,1544]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figures 8–14. Stegana (Steganina) jiajinshanensis sp. nov., Ƌ. (8) Epandrium (epan), surstylus (sur) and cercus (cerc) (lateral view); (9) surstylus (ventral view); (10) 10th sternite; (11, 12) hypandrium (hypd), parameres (pm), aedeagus (aed) and aedeagal apodeme (aed a) (ventral and lateral view); (13, 14) gonopods (ventral and lateral view). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5216814" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5216814/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="1913">Figure 10</figureCitation>
); dorsal projection of gonopods strongly protruded in lateral view, round at tip (
<figureCitation box="[871,978,855,879]" captionStart="Figures 8–14" captionStartId="5.[212,289,1586,1608]" captionTargetBox="[212,1172,905,1543]" captionTargetId="figure-176@5.[212,1172,903,1544]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figures 8–14. Stegana (Steganina) jiajinshanensis sp. nov., Ƌ. (8) Epandrium (epan), surstylus (sur) and cercus (cerc) (lateral view); (9) surstylus (ventral view); (10) 10th sternite; (11, 12) hypandrium (hypd), parameres (pm), aedeagus (aed) and aedeagal apodeme (aed a) (ventral and lateral view); (13, 14) gonopods (ventral and lateral view). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5216814" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5216814/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="1913">Figure 14</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5216814" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5216814" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5216814/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="1913" startId="5.[212,289,1586,1608]" targetBox="[212,1172,905,1543]" targetPageId="5">
